name: ORDER 5 WORD SQUARE
description: Word squares are fun to play with. This particular one stemmed from the word HEART, which is a common thread in everything we as humans do. We love and listen from the heart. I suppose someone could create a fictional narrative to this one, but there is no real meaning intended. Pure word abstraction at it's best/worst depending on your take on this type of work. Though to be candid, if you made it this far in the book...it's safe to say you're picking up what I'm throwing down. lol
